<div class="title">
  <h1>Rabbit Search Game</h1>
</div>
<div class="description-wrapper">
  <div class="rabbit-gif-wrapper">
    <img class="rabbit-gif" src="https://media.tenor.com/Add9qffI-NgAAAAC/rabbit-stare.gif" alt="Rabbit Gif">
    <img class="tenor-footer" src="/img/tenor/PB_tenor_logo_blue_horizontal.svg" alt="Tenor Footer">
  </div>
  <div class="description">
    <p>
      Choose your own adventure and build upon it! Your choices were built by players,
      and you can continue the chain. Everyone starts on the same starting point. Every
      scenario presents a short story, a fitting GIF, and three branching choices. Can
      you explore them all?
    </p>
    <form action="/scene/0" method="GET">
      <button class="button" type="submit">Enter Rabbit Hole</button>
    </form>
    <p class="total">There are a total of <%= locals.static.scene_count || 0 %> paths</p>
  </div>
</div>